---
title: Chicken & Creamy Thyme Sauce with Rosemary-Roasted Potatoes & Garlicky Veggies
description: It’s all about the sauce in this winning dinner – garlic and thyme combine in a creamy and delectable sauce that’s
rich and indulgent. Teamed with succulent chicken, rosemary potatoes and garlicky veggies, you just can’t go wrong.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
